                h2 Doe jij dit beter? 
                a(href="#calculate-emissions") Bereken jouw uitstoot!
            section(id="calculate-emissions")
                form(method="post", action="/result")
                    section(class="orange")
                        div(class="section-header")
                            h2 Openbaar vervoer 
                            span &#x1F6A0;
                        p Vul hier je reiskilometers in als je met het openbaar vervoer naar school reist.
                        div(class="divider")
                        div
                            label(for="train") Trein
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="train", value="0", type="number", name="train", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="bus") Bus
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="bus", value="0", type="number", name="bus", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="subway") Metro
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="subway", value="0", type="number", name="subway", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="tram") Tram
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="tram", value="0", type="number", name="tram", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                        div(class="divider")
                    section(class="yellow")
                        div(class="section-header")
                            h2 Tweewielers
                            span ðŸ›µ
                        p Vul hier je reiskilometers in als je met een tweewieler naar school reist.
                        div(class="divider")
                        div
                            label(for="motorcycle") Motor
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="motorcycle", value="0", type="number", name="motorcycle", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="gasScooter") Benzine scooter
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="gasScooter", value="0", type="number", name="gasScooter", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="electricScooter") Elektrische scooter
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="electricScooter", value="0", type="number", name="electricScooter", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="electricBike") Elektrische fiets
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="electricBike", value="0", type="number", name="electricBike", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                        div(class="divider bottom-divider")
                    section(class="purple") 
                        div(class="section-header")
                            h2 Auto's
                            span ðŸš˜
                        p Vul hier je reiskilometers in als je met de auto naar school reist.
                        div(class="divider")
                        div 
                            label(for="gasCar") Benzine auto
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="gasCar", value="0", type="number", name="gasCar", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="dieselCar") Diesel auto
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="dieselCar", value="0", type="number", name="dieselCar", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="hybridCar") Hybride auto 
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="hybridCar", value="0", type="number", name="hybridCar", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                            label(for="electricCar") Elektrische auto
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="electricCar", value="0", type="number", name="electricCar", min="0", max="100")
                                span km
                        div(class="divider bottom-divider")
                    section(class="orange")
                        h2 Reisdagen per week
                        p Vul hier het aantal gemiddeld aantal reisdagen dat je per week naar school gaat in. Bij de berekening wordt er van 38 lesweken per jaar uitgegaan.
                        div(class="divider")
                        div
                            label(for="days") Dagen per week
                            div(class="input-container")
                                input(id="days", value="1", type="number", name="days", min="1", max="5")
                                span(id="last-span") Dagen
                        div(id="submit-container")
                            input(type="submit", value="Bereken mijn uitstoot!")
                        div(class="divider bottom-divider")